    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A pair of heavy stones or metal spheres attached with a chain or rope, usually thrown to tie enemies legs together.</p><p><strong>Special.</strong> In addition to taking damage, a Medium or smaller creature hit by a bola must make a DC 15 Dexterity saving throw. On a failure, the target is immobilized until the end of its next turn. A bola has no additional effect on creatures that are formless, or creatures that are Large or larger.</p>",
